('1255','English','Allows to create a chart of account structure and create prime entry books. Journal entries can be added for a financial year and if required based on locations. Trial balance, balance sheet and profit and lose accounts can be generated as reports with di'),
('1256','English','Admin and a normal user roles available with default user role permissions. New users can be created for type of admin or normal user. When required additional user roles can be created with custom permissions and can be assigned to users. Module is compl'),
